lead_paragraph: Pakistan's hopes of continuing their unbeaten run in seven consecutive test series will come under pressure when they face a resurgent New Zealand in the second and final test in Hamilton without inspirational skipper Misbah-ul-Haq.

headline.print_headline: New Zealand Wary of Pakistan Backlash in Hamilton
